{"tid":1478824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港人入］8.18 人數好重要，但理性係關鍵","createTime":"2019-08-16T16:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T16:40:26.000Z","uid":279111,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47fcb620449ec26824db4c0b03ee4dcfe8692493","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"8.18 會有幾多鬼我唔知<br />\n<br />\n個風係咪純白色恐怖我唔知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我唯一知嘅 就係</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個人入場都要保持理性</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔主動   上裝<br />\n唔主動   拎野掟狗車（用口屌下佢倒是可以的）<br />\n唔主動   set road block打游擊<br />\n唔主動   過夜<br />\n唔主動   捉鬼（邊個衝邊個就係鬼）<br />\n唔主動   打鬼（綁起佢倒是可以的）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有人喺冇事發生嘅情況下set road block，請阻止，多人且和理非下自然會塞爆，唔使road block。寥然砌road block只會令氣氛緊張，然後會有人上裝，鬼就容易做野了。</span><br />\n<br />\n今次行完，直接走冇問題，唔好叫人留。<br />\n<br />\n裝係可以帶，但要減低戴嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非主場。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要記住，即使你係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武</span>，都請你以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非</span>身分上場。好多一家大細出黎行，唔可以令佢地受驚食蛋，唔可以令佢地唔敢再出黎。多一個，多好多。<br />\n<br />\n要記住，呢一次係一場<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公關民意戰</span>，係要話比全世界知 香港人對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自由</span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民主</span>有幾大渴求。唔好比黑警同鬼 spin走左。<br />\n<br />\n要記住，<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非 &gt; 死線 &gt; 升級（勇武）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 維園見</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNrEeMD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNrEeMD.png&h=0c99d02f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59310cddc926ca1bf65b5900bb354c0a193dfbdb","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:12:53.000Z","msg":"8.18 保持理性"},{"pid":"7c404bf656c9c7a6115ecd4bfab625d510a28b14","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"8.18 和理非"},{"pid":"f71d43434285e674ae799c64ab21be2d5ec5b3ab","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"8.18 維園見"},{"pid":"b7bb850e770ce9e8d30dbb9c61f81ae70a24f0da","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:13:50.000Z","msg":"8.18 黎次300萬"},{"pid":"f845c3351ec3d54de985c9f856d2ce62699c7655","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:14:09.000Z","msg":"8.18 鬼有乜好怕"},{"pid":"47ff39e9578f9e6a40705418e3f69658231862b4","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"8.18 設死線"},{"pid":"1fe50162980b525b8a0aeadcd9f909c854d55ffa","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"8.18 民意公關戰"},{"pid":"e77beacab09836344a722829c183f52a551baecf","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"8.18 推我上去"},{"pid":"0443045eee2b43606b918e4caf0df9e2fc69fa71","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"8.18 帶gear，避免戴gear"},{"pid":"4df90fcbe62320fd4b644f6a41cb3eeb12e97ef1","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"8.18 最後一推"},{"pid":"cb76a4403423c879226dcfd5eea60ef840b1f26a","tid":1478824,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"真係冇人睇架喎"},{"pid":"6f96f8c462